            <li><a href="#faq" class="hover:text-indigo-600 transition-colors">SAT Scoring FAQ</a></li>
            <li><a href="#calculator" class="hover:text-indigo-600 transition-colors">Score Calculator</a></li>
            <li><a href="/blog/can-you-use-a-calculator-on-the-sat" class="hover:text-indigo-600 transition-colors">Calculator Guide</a></li>
